                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Minister <persName type="from">Barrett</persName> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Bogotá</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1905-12-20">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 20, 1905</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Barrett reports that an official announcement has been made of the discovery
                    of a plot to dispose of the President of Colombia and to organize a new
                    government. Many prominent men who were arrested are now about to undergo trial
                    by court-matrial. Among the leaders are a former cabinet minister and
                    generals.)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
